      "message": "I think if someone is genuinely doing this externally, then there\u0027s a lot of details here that I left out because it will really depend on their setup (e.g. where/how to push). Thus, I\u0027m not sure it\u0027s worth spelling those things out when the exact instructions could get stale (due to k8s updates) or be unhelpful (for people with a very different setup)\n\nI\u0027ve linked to our dockerfiles and the kubernetes configs so people can see what we\u0027ve done, and I think that\u0027s the best we can do without becoming technical writers.",
